Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願っても何もできないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}わかってはいるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}失う怖さが邪魔をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}誰しも明日へ向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}見えない 知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}自由も愛も与えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}さぁ選べ  舞い降りた天使達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}感じる予感に Shoot the arrow of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:41.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}翼に意志を 身を委ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}倦まず弛まず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただ 生きてたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}もう いっそ嘘でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}正義を貫く 最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}「幸せになりたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:03:02.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}ただそれだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}It ain’t over till it’s over(Shoot!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往邁進 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:18.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}即使祈願 也什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.41,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}明明知道如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.12,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}哪怕失去的恐懼作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.58,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}人們還是會走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}看不見 不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.21,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}給他自由與愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}好了 選擇吧 飛舞降臨的天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}向察覺的預感 射出命運之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:41.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}灌注意志於翅膀  委身於它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不知疲倦 從不鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}只是 想要活著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}不管了 就算撒謊也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}貫穿正義 到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.19,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}說一句「我想要幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:03:02.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.95,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}它不會結束 直到它結束 (發射!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.75,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur3}勇往直前 GO!
